title: Rand Paul’s campaign releases ominous, optimistic strategy memo
text: Thursday morning, the presidential campaign of Sen. Rand Paul (R-Ky.) began distributing a memo from manager Chip Englander pushing back on " some in the media who are pushing a false narrative that Senator Rand Paul is on the ropes. " What followed was a rundown of Paul's organizing efforts on campuses and in early states, including […] ...
